name: "Seasoned Brown" iPad Mini Case
description:
Drop resistant and made with the finest sustainable PU leather giving you the same feel like that of leather but with the added benefit of being at an affordable price.

Includes FREE screen protector for both front and back as well as screen wiper to help keep your loved tablet clean.

Free UK delivery and shipped to you within 3 - 5 working days.
